        &nbsp;
        Transparent encryption
      %p Cryodex transparently encrypts data before it leaves your servers, while preserving the ability to find, search and sort records in the cloud.
    .large-4.column
      %h4
        %i.icon-tasks
        &nbsp;
        Real-time audit trails
      %p Keep track of who accessed what with detailed logs and audit trails. Cryodex is a turnkey solution for HIPAA and PCI-DSS compliance requirements.
    .large-4.column
      %h4
        %i.icon-cloud
        &nbsp;
        Power of the cloud
      %p Cryodex enables the cloud for businesses. Integrate with the cloud storage provider of your choice and keep closed-door security.
  .row.features.spacy
    .large-4.column
      %h4.no-top-margin
        %i.icon-check
        &nbsp;
        Easy integration
      %p Integrate Cryodex in your existing application in less than 5 lines of code. Our security gateway works behind the scenes to protect your data and never gets in your way.
    .large-4.column
      %h4.no-top-margin
        %i.icon-anchor
        &nbsp;
        Preserve function
      %p Security that breaks applications is pointless. We use cutting-edge technology to preserve the format, function and order of encrypted data in the cloud.
    .large-4.column
      %h4.no-top-margin
        %i.icon-random
        &nbsp;
        Any database
      %p Our modular architecture transparently layers on top of any database system, including both NoSQL and traditional SQL storage solutions.
